<br>
Most of the PoP aa's are less than stellar, and realy have about 4 seconds of thought put into all of them.  There are a few nice ones spread out over all the classes, but the vast majority of them are utter and total crap, and I think that's the way VI wants them to be.  They've funneled everyone into about 6 zones in this expansion, and given them garbage aa abilities...they don't want us to be playing EQ anymore, they want us to be maxed out on XP, have the useful AA's and ready to move on to EQ2 when it comes out.<br>
<br>
Hrm, looking back, i guess it's not really devils advocate, since i'm just as cynical about what SoE is doing here too, so screw em. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48986">Marshall Haass Wolvesbane</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71943">Venerable Cagna Soulshaker</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
